title: Initial Commit
message:
Initial Commit

Created a fresh project using the "New Android Application"
wizard in Eclipse.  Used all defaults except as follows:
- Application Name: Share File
- Project Name:     ShareFileApp
- Package Name:     com.abcodeworks.sharefileapp
- Theme: Holo Light
- Uncheck "Create Activity" on "Configure Project" screen.
